As part of the DevOps engineer role we manage the k8s cluster for our organization and ensure that applications are deployed and there are no issues with the application we have set up monitoring on the Kubernetes cluster. we ensure that whenever there are bugs for example developers are stuck with pods and services they are not able to route the traffic inside the k8's cluster in such cases we came into the picture and solve the problem, we have 3 masters and 10 workers nodes, we have to do continuous maintenance activity on the 10 worker nodes like patching. we also serve as SMEs if anyone in the organization creates a JIRA/ticket and we will help them in solving and making them in understanding Kubernetes
